 Isibalo sabantu asebefile ngenxa yeCovid-19 sesikhuphukele ku3 860. "Abanye abawu140 sebeshonile. Abawu11 abaKwaZulu-Natal, abawu24 abase-Eastern Cape, abawu39 abaseGauteng kanti abawu66 abaseWestern Cape," kusho uMkhize.  Isibalo sabantu asebesindile singu118 232, okusho ukuthi sesiwu47.2%. Sesisonke esabantu esebehloliwe sesingu2 057 232 sekubandakanya nesisanda kwenziwa sabangu56 663.